            Let's Start a Conversation
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Whether you're looking to streamline your invoicing, manage projects more efficiently, or just want to chat about your business needs, we're here to help.
          </p>
        </div>

        <%# Contact cards %>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <%# Email card %>
